<section id="selectdataarea">
    <h1 id="hd_id171697546202709"><variable id="h1"><link href="text/scalc/01/SelectData.xhp">Select Data Area</link></variable></h1>
    <paragraph id="par_id821697546202712" role="paragraph">Selects the data area where the cursor or selection is located.</paragraph>
</section>
    <section id="howtoget">
        <embed href="text/scalc/00/00000402.xhp#selectdataarea"/>
    </section>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id911697547125155">To select the data area, the cursor must be inside or adjacent to a block of data.</paragraph>

<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id21697547130354">If the cursor is not adjacent to a block of data, the selection returns the cell where the cursor is placed.</paragraph>

<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id391697547137174">If the cell is adjacent to two blocks of data, the selection is the rectangular area that wraps the two blocks of data.</paragraph>
